high_descs: Walk forward to the chair, turn to the left, and walk to the table that is in the corner of the room.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Turn to the left, walk to the furthest wall, turn to the right, and walk to the end table.
Turn on the lamp that is on the in table.
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a newspaper.

high_descs: Turn left and walk around to the far side of the round dining table
Pick up the newspaper from the table
Turn left and walk across the room then turn right and approach the small wooden side table
Turn on the lamp on the side table
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper under the light of the lamp

high_descs: Walk around the table to the trashcan and face the table.
Turn around, walk across the room to the wall, turn right, and walk to the lamp table.
anns.task_desc: Look at the newspaper under the lamp.
